'''''Minnow Hawk''''' was the name of a model in the [[Museum of Flight]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Harridan (planet)|Harridan]]. Though it resembled a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler's]] [[Starship/Legends|starship]], the description marked it as a primitive glider incapable of flight for more than 20 seconds at a time, only if there was no wind.

